workspace 1 output HDMI3
workspace 2 output HDMI1
workspace 3 output HDMI3
workspace 4 output HDMI1
workspace 5 output HDMI3
workspace 6 output HDMI1
workspace 7 output HDMI3
workspace 8 output HDMI1
workspace 9 output HDMI3
workspace 10 output HDMI1